content.rendered:
Directed by Rohit Dhawan.

Written by Tushar Hiranandani. Hussain Dalal.

Cast John Abraham(Kabir Shergill). Varun Dhawan(Junaid Ansari). Jacqueline Fernandez(Ishika). Akshaye Khanna(Wagah). Rahul Dev(Altaf). Saqib Saleem(Viraj Sharma). Vijay Raaz(Khabri Chacha). Akshay Kumar(Sameer Gazi). Rashmi Nigam(Mrs. Wagah). Nargis Fakhri(Samaira Dalal). Tarun Khanna(Saeed Naqvi). Parineeti Chopra(Muskaan). Satish Kaushik(Quereshi (voice)). Tirth(Viraj Sharma Fan (Kid)). Atul Wassan(India vs Pakistan (Commentator 2) (as Atul Waswani)). Ramiz Raja(Self (Commentator 1)). Omar Hassan(TSA Agent). Valeria(Airport Counter Lady). Darsheel(Wagah’s Kid). Deepna Kumar(Birthday Girl). Ashu Sharma(Kamlesh Bhai). Deepak Kumar Verma(Abudin Bartender (as Deepak Verma)). Amin(Abudin Kid). Heydar Heman(SWAT Officer 1). Mir Sarwar(Abudin Arms Dealer). Hisham(Abudin Border Security Chief). Mohamed Nmilla(Abudin Truck Driver). Akash Dhar(Wagah Man). Aamir Yaseen(Hussain). Jitin Gaur(Rashid). Maximus(Bradman). Kashyap Kapoor(Sketch Artist). Mushtaq Kak(Supermarket Owner). Adam Stone(SWAT Officer 2 (as Adam Stone)). Anupriya Goenka(Alishka Iyer). Sahil Phull(Vishal Sinha (as Sahil Phull)). Manu Malik(Suited Man in Lift). Aasia(UAE Foreign Affairs Minister’s PA). Sameer(UAE Foreign Affairs Minister). Faisal Rashid(Pakistani Cricket Fan). Madhur Arora(External Affairs Minister’s PA). Mona Ambegaonkar(External Affairs Minister of India). Pawan Chopra(BCCI President). Mohinder Amarnath(Self (Indian Cricket Team Coach)). K.T.(Indian Cricket Team Junior Physio).Digvijay Purohit. Aakash Chopra(India vs Sri Lanka (Commentator 2) (as Aakash Chopra)). Pommi Mbangwa(India vs Sri Lanka (Commentator 1) (as Pommie Mbangwa)). Mansoor Al-Fili(Captain (as Mansoor)) . Teena Paradkar(Dancer). Prateek Saxena(Clubber). Harsh Shashwat(Media Promoter). Manish Soni(Munni’s Frind). Nikhil Sonkeshariya(Unknown). Erand Hoxha(Capo (uncredited)). Syed Shujat(Beach / Pool Buddy (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Paul W. Baker. Hicham Hajji. Hamid Herraf. Sunil Lulla. Rakesh Madhotra. Manoj Mittra. Sajid Nadiadwala. Mini Purushot.

Production H Films. Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment.
